title: 2021 North 1 Region wrestling: Final results (Reg. 1 & 2)
body: 2021 NJSIAA / Rothman Orthopaedic North 1 region wrestling tournamentThe best high school boys wrestlers in New Jersey open pursuit of state titles on Saturday with the opening round of the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament.The North Jersey, Section 1 Region tournament is set for Mount Olive High School.Complete results are on the way from , so stay tuned.The final round:2-, Mount Olive d. 1-, River Dell, 3-0.1-, Roxbury p. 6-, Bergen Catholic, 3:41.1-, Kinnelon d. 2-, St. Joseph (Mont.), 7-0.1-, Bergen Catholic d. 2-, Westwood, 7-1.2-, Boonton d. 1-, Don Bosco Prep, 3-1.1-, St. Joseph (Mont.) d. 3-, Bergen Catholic, 10-4.1-, St. Joseph (Mont.) md. 3-, Boonton, 12-3.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
